# Willow & Water Project Standards

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: React with Vite
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Icons**: Lucide Icons

## Design System

### Aesthetic
"Organic High-End" — clean, natural, sophisticated

### Color Palette

| Name     | Hex       | Usage                        |
|----------|-----------|------------------------------|
| Sage     | `#71797E` | Primary accent, buttons      |
| Bone     | `#F9F6EE` | Backgrounds, light surfaces  |
| Charcoal | `#36454F` | Text, dark elements          |

### Typography

- **Headings**: Playfair Display (serif)
- **Body**: Inter (sans-serif)

```jsx
// Example heading
<h1 className="font-playfair text-charcoal">...</h1>

// Example body text
<p className="font-inter text-charcoal">...</p>
```

## SEO Requirements

- Use semantic HTML tags: `<header>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<nav>`, `<footer>`
- Every `<img>` must have descriptive `alt` text
- Use proper heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)

## Code Organization

- Keep components **under 200 lines**
- Separate business logic from UI presentation
- Extract reusable logic into custom hooks
